</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ECM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P2128: Throttle / Pedal Position Sensor / Switch “E” Circuit High
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Output voltage of APP sensor (sub) signal circuit is higher than 2.50 V.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(1 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
